<page>
    <shortlink>form layout button properties properties</shortlink>
    <topic>FormView Button Properties</topic>
    <description>The Button Properties define the layout of the content shown on the button (text and/or image) as well as the button's id, help text, and whether or not the button is visible or disabled.</description>
    <sections>
        <section>
            <title>Bubble help</title>
            <description>
                <p>Specify the bubble help shown for the button.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Button layout</title>
            <description>
                <p>The *[ui:Button layout]* property defines the layout of the button in the FormView's layout. The layout can include text, an image, or both. The following layout options are available:</p>
            </description>
            <list bullet='true'>
                <item>
                    <name>Text only</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Image only</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Text followed by Image</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Image followed by text</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Image above text</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Text above image</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Text left &amp; image right</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>Image left &amp; text right</name>
                </item>
            </list>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Button text</title>
            <description>
                <p>The text shown in the button.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Enable expression</title>
            <description>
                <p>An expression that defines whether or not the button is enabled.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Id</title>
            <description>
                <p>The ID of the button.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Image name</title>
            <description>
                <p>The image shown on the button. The image can be an SVG icon, CSS icon, an image defined in the project, or a built-in Alpha Anywhere image.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Show/hide expression</title>
            <description>
                <p>An expression that defines whether or not the button is visible.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
    </sections>
</page>
